comments: Does not give a letter grade on any of the written assignments. Narrative evaluations on written work were very fair but hard to know what that equated to in terms of a letter grade. So you never knew where you stood until you got your final grade.She does, however, answer questions quickly and returns papers within 2 weeks.

I too, do not I understand her point to not grading papers-I worked really hard, and would have appreciated a grade. She could have participated more, but was helpful when I asked for it. She is "just okay" and so is the class...though some of the material can be difficult.

human service delivery was DIFFICULT!!! BASES ALL ASSIGNMENTS and DISCUSSIONS ON A FOCAL AGENCY YOU HAVE TO INTERVIEW!!!! DOESNT GRADE ANY PAPERS AT ALL!!!! leaves you guessing where you stand feedback is great but not a grade!!! WRITING INTENSIVE AND CRITICAL OF GRAMMAR... not a teacher i would take again....
